Hyderabad: 6 killed in fire in cooler godown Hyderabad: 6 killed in fire in cooler godown At least six persons were killed after a devastating fire broke out in cooler godown in Hyderabad, according to ANI report. By: FE Online | New Delhi | Updated: February 22, 2017 9:20 AM At least six persons were killed after a devastating fire broke out in cooler godown in Hyderabad, according to ANI report. 
At least six persons were killed after a devastating fire broke out in cooler godown in Hyderabad, according to ANI report. It has been learned that 6 bodies were recovered from the spot. Four fire tenders have manged to douse the flame. The cause behind the fire is yet to be ascertained. Please Wait while comments are loading...
